name: BiP Channel Asset Collection Website
description:
This website is for asset collection. This design was created to make is super easy for the user to provide their assets for their channel in a better way.


The UI was designed with the intention of having it seem as though they were developing the channel themselves but in a much easier way.


Created By

My name is Akeema Williamson, and I am UI UX designer with a passion in creating unique websites and mobile applications.


For the past 5 years I have taught myself this craft and have designed dozens of sites and applications.


You can view more of my work on Behance and Dribble.
